title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Bell 407 - starting the heli
description:
In this video we will go through the process of starting the engine of the Bell 407 helicopter. We will soon figure out that the highlighting of the buttons when clicking the eye icon in the checklist doesn't work but at the end we have a running engine.
